Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.28,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,我是阿曼達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.74,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,跟妳一樣同是叛逆之士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.58,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,來好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.79,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.38,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,妳這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.17,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,等一下 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.01,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.60,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 就沒有我駕馭不了的掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.36,Default,W,0,0,0,,現在以極大優勢領先的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.23,Default,W,0,0,0,,「菇毒女王{Mushroom Poison Queen}」蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.23,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,654)}Mushroom Poison Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.57,Default,A,0,0,0,,蘇西 這邊這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.82,Default,S,0,0,0,,亞可 要上囉
