Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.41,Default,W,0,0,0,,亞可？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.91,Default,W,0,0,0,,亞可騎著掃帚飛過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:29.66,Default,S,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.75,Default,D,0,0,0,,亞可？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.51,Default,W,0,0,0,,現第三名是「脫韁黑馬{Dark Horse}野丫頭」阿曼達！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.51,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,654)}Dark Horse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.72,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,那是我的掃帚 快還我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.77,Default,W,0,0,0,,阿曼達出局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.36,Default,W,0,0,0,,是交接棒失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.65,Default,W,0,0,0,,接到的不是手環而是甜甜圈{Donuts}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.65,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(805.467,654)}Donuts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.95,Default,W,0,0,0,,意想不到的展開
